    "description": "Lee's sister has been kidnapped.<br>The Shadow Circus is in town.<br>This is not a coincidence.<br>Let's go rescue her.<br><br>Kung Fu Er San is a 2D retro pixel side-scrolling beat 'em up, inspired by classic games and martial arts films.<br>You take control of Lee Shao, a talented Shaolin Kung Fu Master whose sister has been kidnapped.<br>To rescue her, Lee must fight his way through side-scrolling levels full of traps, thugs, obstacles and surprises, and master his punches and kicks to defeat all the members of the Shadow Circus, a gang of evil circus artists, with crazy unique powers and fighting skills.<br>The path is arduous, so are the fights.<br>Do you think you have what it takes?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single player Arcade mode;<br></li><li>2 players Versus mode;<br></li><li>Action/adventure levels and one-on-one fighting levels;<br></li><li>Unlockable characters;<br></li><li>Unlockable Hard Mode;<br></li><li>Refined gameplay;<br></li><li>Simple controls;<br></li><li>Playable with keyboard or gamepads;<br></li><li>Steam achievements;<br></li><li>Many references, gags and surprises.</li></ul>",
